The ForC_Cirriculum includes:

ForC_lessons.docx: (Start here), a guide for instructors. Includes required materials mentioned in handouts and referenced by PPT slides. Make sure to check material list for each lesson
ForC_PPT.pptx: PowerPoint slides 

Background_documents: Background for instructors and interested students not necessary for most lessons, but can be incorporated 

Handout_documents: Lesson documents, can distributed to students digitally or as prints

Resources: Lagest folder, can be digitally distributed as is, we don't suggest printing every document. Within it there is folder that contains background reading in the form of scientific publications on carbon cycling, handpainted diagrams of carbon cycling, and more detailed documents.
